вҠў add
  given a вүЎ 3
  given b вүЎ 5
  yield sum

  вҲҙ Compute В«aВ» + В«bВ».

  вҠЁ sum = В«aВ» + В«bВ»

вҠў double
  given addвҶ’sum
  yield result

  вҲҙ Compute В«addвҶ’sumВ» Г— 2.

  вҠЁ result = В«addвҶ’sumВ» Г— 2

вҠў format
  given doubleвҶ’result
  yield text

  вҲҙ Format В«doubleвҶ’resultВ» as "The answer is В«doubleвҶ’resultВ»."

  вҠЁ text = "The answer is " + str(В«doubleвҶ’resultВ») + "."

